    <div class="">
      <% flash.each do |name, message| %>
        <div class="alert alert-<%= name %> alert-dismissible" role="alert">
        <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="alert" aria-label="Close"><span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span></button>
        <p><%= message %></p>
      <% end %>
    </div>
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-12 img-responsive">
            <%= image_tag("https://s3.us-east-2.amazonaws.com/cfdshopnumbers/images/CFD-Scramble-Gold-Leaf-with-Black-Outline.jpg") %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-12">
            <h1 class="pg-title text-center">Chicago Fire Department Shops Numbering Program</h1>
            <h1 class="pg-title text-center">1923 - present</h1>
          </div>
        </div>
        <i class="fa fa-bars" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        <hr>
        <div class="mouseover">
          <p class="hoverbox" id="a-drop">Sedans</p>
          <p class="hoverbox" id="avf-drop">Airport</p>
          <p class="hoverbox" id="b-drop">Coupes, Wagons, SUVs</p>
          <p class="hoverbox" id="c-drop">Ambulances and Early Squads</p>
          <p class="hoverbox" id="d-drop">Engines</p>
          <p class="hoverbox" id="e-drop">Trucks</p>
          <p class="hoverbox" id="f-drop">Trailers</p>
          <p class="hoverbox" id="g-drop">Squads, Snorkels, and Special Equipment</p>
          <p class="hoverbox" id="h-drop">Reserve Steam Engines (1920s)</p>
          <p class="hoverbox" id="s-drop">Additional Special Equipment</p>
          <p class="hoverbox" id="pre-drop">Vehicles Predating Numbering Program</p>
          <p class="hoverbox" id="fip-drop">Chicago Fire Insurance Patrol</p>
          <p class="hoverbox" id="former-drop">Vehicles transferred to other departments</p>
          <p class="hoverbox" id="unclass-drop">Singular vehicles</p>
          <p class="hoverbox" id="unid-drop">Shop numbers yet to be identified</p>
        </div>
        <div class="row" id="main-buttons">
          <nav id="nav" class="col-12">
            <ul class="main-first">
              <li id="a"><a href="a-series" class="btn-default">A- series</a></li>
              <li id="avf"><a href="avf-series" class="btn-default">AVF- series</a></li>
              <li id="b"><a href="b-series" class="btn-default">B- series</a></li>
              <li id="c"><a href="c-series" class="btn-default">C- series</a></li>
              <li id="d"><a href="d-series" class="btn-default">D- series</a></li>
              <li id="e"><a href="e-series" class="btn-default">E- series</a></li>
              <li id="f"><a href="f-series" class="btn-default">F- series</a></li>
              <li id="g"><a href="g-series" class="btn-default">G- series</a></li>
              <li id="h"><a href="h-series" class="btn-default">H- series</a></li>
              <li id="s"><a href="s-series" class="btn-default">S- series</a></li>
            </ul>
            <ul class="main-second">
              <li id="pre"><a href="pre-shop" class="btn-default">Pre-1923</a></li>
              <li id="fip"><a href="fip" class="btn-default">Fire Insurance Patrol</a></li>
              <li id="former"><a href="former" class="btn-default">Former CFD</a></li>
              <li id="unclass"><a href="unclassified" class="btn-default">Unclassified</a></li>
              <li id="unid"><a href="unidentified" class="btn-default">Unidentified</a></li>
            </ul>
            <ul class="main-second">
              <li id="roster"><a href="roster" class="btn-default">Daily Apparatus Roster</a></li>
            </ul>
          </nav>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <main class="col-12 text-center">
            <p>The Chicago Fire Department's shops numbering program began around January 1923 while the department was in the final stages of complete motorization. The last response with horse-drawn equipment would occur on February 5, 1923. Department-owned motorized equipment was to be cataloged by vehicle size and function, and some of these definitions would change in later years.</p>
            <p id="search-query">Looking for a specific record?</p>
          </main>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-12 text-center">
            <%= form_tag "/search", method: :post do %>
              <%= text_field_tag :search, nil, placeholder: 'e.g. D-361', :required => 'required' %>
              <%= submit_tag "Search" %>
            <% end %>
          </div>
        </div>
        </div>
        <hr>
        <footer>
          <div class="col-12">
            <p class="text-right">An Eric Biel project, 2016-2021<br>
            Sincere thanks to the<a href="http://www.firemuseumofgreaterchicago.org/index.html">Fire Museum of Greater Chicago</a></p>
          </div>
        </footer>
      </div>
